Program: Omnibus
Title: Wild at Heart - African Childhood
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376m4r
Last Broadcast Date: 05 February 2001
Shen Mcknightsky and others talk about their memories of growing up in central Africa, camping out in the bush, with the understanding that they, the human, were intruding on the space of the wild animals.